Naturalization Service, has asked Oakland officials for permission
to renovate a warehouse to serve as a detention facility. The
council is considering the proposal, but the issue was not on
Tuesday night's agenda.
   It was unclear if the protesters belonged to an organization. A
police dispatcher who answered the phone this morning said no one
was available for comment.
